STATE
v.
Jonathan E. BRUNSON 247P16-6 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 9, 2019 Jonathan Eugene Brunson, for Brunson, Jonathan Eugene. Sherri Horner Lawrence, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 27th of February 2019 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of May 2019."
